These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, august, june, december
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Birthday      | june  | august | december        | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, sunflower, orchid
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who growssunflower##7
2. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
3. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Flower     | sunflower | zinnia       | orchid         | balloon-flower     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, hamster, rabbit
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the chinchilla##7
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Pet   | hamster | chinchilla  | rabbit   | pony |

