.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, d&b, blues, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the fan of hip-hop##7
3. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | reggae | hip-hop       | blues |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

