.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, reading, rock-climbing, video-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, poppy, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing   | video-games | reading |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | sunflower | balloon-flower      | poppy |

