.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dannemann, game, ritmeester
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, indonesian, nigerian
1. the game-smoker is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
6. the nigerian is somewhere between the american and the dutch##7
7. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar      | dannemann | tiparillo      | game | ritmeester     |
| Nationality   | american    | nigerian | dutch   | indonesian |

