.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
City: berlin, nizza, rome, edinburgh
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, spanish
1. the argentine is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left or far right##3
4. the spanish is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to rome##7
5. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| City          | edinburgh    | berlin   | nizza | rome  |
| Nationality   | argentine | nigerian | spanish    | chinese |

