.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, old-henry, blend, montecristo
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the old-henry-smoker is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the horse##1
4. the blend-smoker is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##7
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar   | montecristo | blend | old-henry | bolivar |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

