.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, thriller, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, salsa, classical, funk
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the fan of funk##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the fan of classical##6
3. the fan of salsa is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
5. the person watching family movies is the fan of jazz##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Music-Genre           | jazz    | salsa   | funk  | classical      |

