2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person drinking sprite##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | hiking | collecting | filmmaking | fishing |
| Beverage   | cola   | iced-tea      | sprite        | lemonade  |

