4. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
