3. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the dunhill-smoker##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the chaman-smoker and the havana-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
