2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary    | superhero | satire     | romance |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 